    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="TextAnnotation_14rdnv0">
      <bpmn:text>Check if the user was created by a first buy on an external system (like Shopify). The state of the transaction will be sent with the welcome email, so we ignore this notification for the first transaction of this user.</bpmn:text>
